<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n10052c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10052c">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10052c"> 52(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Lyons mail</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">En 1723, <mark>le courrier de Lyon</mark> arrivait &agrave; Paris trois fois par semaine; celui de Toulouse, une fois par semaine; celui d&apos;Espagne, tous les quinze jours. <font color="green">[In 1723 the mail from Lyons arrived in Paris three times a week; that from Toulouse once; and that from Spain every fortnight.]</font> <small> Eug&egrave;ne Gallois, <a name="EGLP" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#EGLP"><cite title="source">La Poste</cite></a> (1894) 118</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
